><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">目前平台均为人工审核作品，以防违法、广告等信息污染平台环境。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">PS：目前均为人工审核，我们会尽快改进审核机制，达到发布5分钟内完成审核的速度标</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">准，敬请期待。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">6</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品审核需要多长时间？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">工作日（白天09:00至19:00）审核时间不超过2小时，节假日和晚间审核时间不超过24小时。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">7</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">可以编辑/删除我上传的作品吗？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">可以，但是参赛作品不允许删除哦。如需取消活动参与，请私信联系客服</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">【客服昵称】</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">三、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">平台推荐</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">相关</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">8</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">平台推荐设计师有哪些特权？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">发布的作品更容易获得高展示位，获得更多曝光量</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台的征集作品活动、商业合作机会将优先获得消息与合作邀请</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">9</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何成为平台推荐设计师？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">在发布的作品数量达到5个时，平台会对创作者进行一次评定，评定结果将决定是否能够成为平台推荐设计师。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、评定维度：作品质量为主，作品类型、作品点赞率、评论率、商业合作性等为辅。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、平台会定期对创作者进行重新评定，视情况维持推荐或撤销推荐。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">10</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品推荐是什么？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台会定期或审核时，将最近的作品进行质量等级评定，优秀的作品会得到平台更高的首页展示位支持。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">11</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何获得作品推荐？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品质量高；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品完成度高；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品具有独特的表达手法；</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">、</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品对其他的设计师有帮助，有启发，有激励</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">推荐作品还会以作者用心的程度、网友好评度等作为参考，客观推荐。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt 28.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:-28.5pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">四、</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">赚钱必读指南</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">12</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">什么是平台供稿人？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台供稿人是创作者与平台建立的一种【供稿→收购】的商业合作关系，旨在于为创作者提供一条可赚取高收益的道路。认证后创作者将于平台签订协议，在双方达成一致的前提下，平台通过征集形式购买创作者提供的供稿作品及其著作权。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">13</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">为什么要认证供稿人？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">因供稿作品的买卖，需双方签订协议才构成合法商业行为，故需要创作者提供相关个人/企业信息并认证后，创作者才有资格参与征集活动。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">PS：即使认证成为平台供稿人，你仍然拥有所上传作品著作权，只有当平台正式录用作品后，该作品的著作权才正式转为平台所有。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">14</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">什么是征集活动？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">平台会将设计需求以征集活动的形式发布在活动页列表，创作者可在活动页列表找寻自己有能力设计创作的活动，制作供稿作品参与活动，经平台认可的作品将会录用并支付相应报酬收益</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">15</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">作品入围有什么用？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品入围代表其已达到该活动要求的录用门槛，但入围并不保证百分百录用，创作者可加入活动群与活动运营咨询录用相关事宜。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、另一方面会将作品展示在活动的入围作品列表，为作品提供一定曝光度。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、非征集类活动的作品入围奖励，请以活动详情的说明为准。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">16</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：什么作品能够入围？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">征集类活动的作品入围评定维度：</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品符合活动说明的要求</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、作品质量、完成度达标</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、作品对后续参与的作品有教学意义、有启发</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">非征集类活动的作品入围标准，请以活动详情的说明为准。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">17</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：如何得知作品入围了？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">作品将会在平台</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">[</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">消息-通知</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">]</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">内发送作品入围通知</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">18</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何确定作品可被录用？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、若作品达到可以录用的标准后，活动运营将会通过私信、电话、QQ（默认私信）与创作者联系，沟通后续录用流程。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、作品入围后，建议创作者加入活动群（在活动详情内有公示），与活动运营咨询；若未达到录用标准，也可及时知晓未录用的原因进行作品调整，直至达到标准后录用。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">19</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何避免多次返工？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、请在参与活动进行作品制作前，详细阅读说明详情，按照规范进行作品设计。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、创作者可以参考已入围或已录用的作品，进一步理解设计方向与规范。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、开始设计前，请下载模板文件认真查看，并按照其规范进行设计。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4、建议创作者加入活动群，可了解其他创作者制作实况，也可与活动运营咨询与作品相关的疑问。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">20</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">录用报价的标准是什么？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">录用价格的评定标准维度：</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">1、作品质量、完成度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">2、符合活动要求的程度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">3、对活动要求理解能力、设计习惯（返工少）</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">4、作品素材完成速度</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt">因活动所征集的作品素材类型不同，各类型的录用价格区间也会不同，但每个征集活动的录用价格区间均会公示至活动详情内。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">Q</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">21</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">：</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold">如何提现？</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">1、在</span><span style="color:#5b9bd5; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">我的收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">页，即可找到提现入口，按流程操作完成后即可提交提现申请</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">2、平台每月15日-25日汇款当月的提现申请。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">3、若是个人提现，实际到账金额=提现金额-税费，税费按当月合计的提前额度计算。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">4、若是企业/机构提现，需寄送提现金额发票；请尽量保证平台在每月汇款期间内收到发票，若在此期间外收到，统一于下个月处理提现汇款。</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">
           </div>

           </div>
            <div class="content_2" v-if="AboutUs">
                <div>
                    <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0">
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">关于我们</span>
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0">
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮</span>
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">圈儿</span>
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">创作者平台，2</span>
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">019</span>
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">年在深圳出身，聚集了数万名优质的设计师、摄影师、插画师等各行业创作者</span>
                        <span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p>
                    <h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">狮</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">圈儿能为你提供什么？</span></h1><h2 style="font-size:12pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">作品展示交流</span></h2><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">作为汇集了各路豪杰创作者的平台，其本身拥有优质的流量用户，以及舒适的同领域交流环境，不但能为每一位创作者提供作品曝光展示，也为创作者之间交流创作提供了良好的媒介。</span></p><h2 style="font-size:12pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">优质作品变现</span></h2><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">“让创作发挥最大价值”，是我们期望在互联网界打造的创作者平台的口号与目标。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">平台会定期发布</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">征集活动，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">无论你的创作技能是绘画、是摄影、是U</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">I</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">设计、甚至是程序员，你都可以在这里</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">找到适合的征集活动，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">获得与创作作品价值相匹配的收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">报酬。</span></p><h2 style="font-size:12pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal">知名企业合作</span></h2><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">与</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">众多一线互联网企业均有商业合作，创作者所设计的作品素材，会经平台征集后，使用在他们的产品上得以呈现。努力帮助创作者的作品获得更大价值，获取更多人认可，也是</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">圈儿一直在做的事情。</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">

            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content_3" v-if="authorization">
                <div><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:center; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">用户协议</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">欢迎使用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">产品！</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">为了更好地为您提供服务，请您仔细阅读《</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户协议》（以下简称“本协议”），本协议是您(以下也可以“用户”来指代您)与</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">深圳掌酷软件有限公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">(以下简称“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">掌酷公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”)就使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品所达成的协议。在您开始使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品之前，请您务必认真阅读并充分理解本协议，如您是</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">未满18周岁</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">未成年人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，请您在法定监护人陪同下仔细阅读并充分理解本协议，并取得法定监护人的同意，特别</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">是</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">涉及免除或者限制</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">责任</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">、开通和使用特殊单项服务的条款。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">除非您完全接受本协议的全部内容，否则您无权使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品。若您使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品，则视为您已充分理解本协议并承诺作为协议的一方当事人接受协议的约束。</span></p><h1 style="margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">1、协议适用范围</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">1.1 本协议约定了</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">掌酷公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">和用户之间就使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品事宜发生的权利义务关系。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">1.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">掌酷公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”指</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">深圳掌酷软件有限公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。但就本协议涉及的某些服务项目，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">掌酷公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的关联企业也可能向您提供服务，与您发生权利义务关系。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">1.3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">指所有直接或间接获取和使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品及相关服务的用户，下称“您”或“用户”。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">1.4</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品指由</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">深圳掌酷软件有限公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">合法拥有并运营的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">网站（</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">w</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">ww.shiquaner.com</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">）。</span></p><h1 style="margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">2、使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">”产品</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">2.1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户可以从任何合法的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">途径登录</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">网站</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">2.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">一旦用户访问“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">网”，即视为使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”产品。为充分实现“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”的全部功能。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    2.3一旦用户上传作品至</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，视为用户同意</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">将其作品用于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">网</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的宣传及推广</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    2.4</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户同意</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权通过本服务将</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">所上传的作品向全世界范围内不特定的网络用户展示，本项权利为永久的、不可撤销的、非排他的授权。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    2.5用户同意作品已经上传，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">则</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">无法控制其传播范围，比如网络用户可能对作品进行复制、下载、修改等。如果</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">不同意本条，则请勿上传作品。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">2.</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">将不定期</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">推出的作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">征集活动，已申请认证为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">平台供稿人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（网签了</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《狮圈儿平台供稿人协议》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">）</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的用户方能参加</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">将对参</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">加活动</span