weight:bold">12、法律管辖</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">12.1本协议的订立、生效、履行、解释及争议的解决均应适用中华人民共和国法律。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">12.2本协议的签署地点为中华人民共和国</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">深圳</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">市</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">南山</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">区，如双方就本协议内容或其执</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">行发生任何争议，双方应尽量友好协商解决；协商不成时，任何一方均可向本协议签署地的人民法院提起诉讼。</span></p><h1 style="margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">13、未成年人使用条款</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">若用户是未满18周岁的未成年人，应在监护人监护、指导并获得监护人同意情况下阅读本协议和使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”及相关服务。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">公司重视对未成年人个人信息的保护，未成年用户在填写个人信息时，请加强个人保护意识并谨慎对待，请在监护人指导时正确使用“</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">”及相关服务。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">未成年用户理解如因您违反法律法规、本协议内容，则您及您的监护人应依照法律规定承担因此而导致的一切后果。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.4未成年人用户特别提示：</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.4.1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">青少年使用本软件及相关服务应该在其监护人的监督指导下，在合理范围内正确学习使用网络，避免沉迷虚拟的网络空间，养成良好上网习惯。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">   </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.4.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">青少年用户必须遵守《全国青少年网络文明公约》：</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（1）要善于网上学习，不浏览不良信息；</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（2）要诚实友好交流，不侮辱欺诈他人；</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（3）要增强自护意识，不随意约会网友；</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（4）要维护网络安全，不破坏网络秩序；</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">（5）要有益身心健康，不沉溺虚拟时空。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">13.5</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">为更好的保护未成年人隐私权益，公司提醒用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">户慎重发布包含未成年人素材的内容，一经发布，即视为用户同意本</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">网站</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">及相关服务展示未成年人的信息、肖像、声音等，且</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">允许</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">依据本协议使用、处理该等与未成年人相关的内容。</span></p><h1 style="margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">14、其他规定</span></h1><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">14.1如本协议中的任何条款无论因何种原因完全或部分无效或不具有执行力，本协议的其余条款仍应有效并且有约束力。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">14.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">您和</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">均是独立的主体，在任何情况下本协议不构成双方之间的代理（单项服务或协议另有约定的除外）、合伙、合营或雇佣关系。</span></p><p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">    </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">14.3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议的版权为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">所有，在法律法规允许的范围内，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">拥有解释和修改的权利</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p></div><div class="cnzz" style="display: none;">
