y:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">至 该账户注销日止。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方所取得的录用作品著作权不因本协议期限届满而终止。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">五</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 双方权利</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1 甲方的权利</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1.1 甲方有权在不通知 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> 的前提下删除作品。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1.2 甲方有权向 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> 申请关闭账户并清算所得的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">平台录用作品的收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1.3 甲方上传</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的作品素材，在被乙方录用前，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">著作权仍归甲方所有</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1.4 甲方在依照乙方要求</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">制作作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">素材</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">上传被录用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">后，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">甲方有权选择买断式或分成式的交易形式，请求</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">按照对应形式的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">计算方式支付报酬</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.1.5 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">甲方有权在</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">查看到不同类型的作品素材的录用价格区间，若该价格区间无法</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">达到甲方的收益预期，甲方有权拒绝乙方的作品素材录用请求。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的权利</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">自作品录用起，甲方将其享有的</span><a name="_cmntref2"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《中华人民共和国著作权法》第十条第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">项至第17项的权利</span></a><a href="#_cmnt2">[A2]</a><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">全部永久转让至乙方,乙方将拥有上述权利，甲方不再拥有，且乙方包括但不限于自行行使或授权其他关联公司、合作伙伴行使。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.2 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">拥有无偿使用甲方作品用于推广和宣传的权利，包括：再利用、复制、分发、发布、转载、上传、邮件、传送、印刷、包装和公开展示作品于任何营销媒介或认为合适的宣传渠道。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">对</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">于甲方已经录用的作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方有权将作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">使用在包括但不限于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">深圳掌酷软件有限公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">及其关联公司的所有现有或将来可能出现的产品和网站中。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">掌酷</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权根据产品的具体需要，对</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">上传的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">已录用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">素材</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">进行必要的修改、编辑、剪辑、汇编、改编等</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，且无需再次通知及额外支付报酬。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.4 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议乙方受许可的权利及于乙方的关联公司（关联公司是指乙方的母子公司、控股、参股以及其他关联公司。以及可能导致公司利益转移关系的其他企业），即乙方的关联公司同等享有录用作品著作权。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.5 乙方对乙方网站及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">享有所有权，并享有相应的域名权、其他知识产权以及有关的一切合法权利。乙方在本服务中提供的内容（包括但不限于网页、文字、图片、音频、视频、图表等）的知识产权属于乙方单独所有。乙方提供本服务时所依托的软件的著作权、专利权及其他知识产权均归乙方及其相应关联公司所有。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">.2.6 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方有权不录用不符合征集活动设计要求的作品素材，且有权不承担甲方在该作品上的任何劳动成本。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.7 乙方有权仅依靠其完全、单独的判断力</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，对即将录用的作品进行评级并</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">决定</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">支付甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的报酬金额。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.8 甲方违反</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">三章3</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">.1.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">项条款</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">时，甲方除了承担</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">该录用作品收益的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10倍的违约金外</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">若造成乙方被第三人索赔或其它损失的，甲方同意全额补偿乙方（包括但不限于各种赔偿费用、律师费及其他合理支出）；乙方如尚有甲方未结报酬的，以上费用可以直接从甲方的报酬中直接抵扣，不足部分甲方应在限期内补足乙方。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.9 当甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的作品素材</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">内容违反法律法规、第三方投诉或举报，乙方有权自行判断</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">停止该作品有关的一切商业行为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，且有权要求甲方限期内提供权属等相关资料、文件予以说明，如未收到符合相关法律规定的资料，乙方有权不予恢复上述删除的素材及信息，且不承担任何责任。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">5.2.10 若甲方停止使用本服务或服务被终止或取消，乙方有权自主决定从服务器上永久地删除甲方数据且无需向甲方返还任何数据。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">六</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 肖像权和物权</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6.1 甲方同意为每一张拥有可辨认的肖像或物权的商业用途作品提供有效、准确的肖像权授权书或</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">知识产</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">权授权书。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6.2 甲方必须保证甲方上传的每一份</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">模特</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">授权书或</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">知识产</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">权授权书真实有效。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6.3 甲方若提供</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">侵权、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">不具有合法来源的作品，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权关闭甲方的帐户，同时</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的客户保留起诉甲方的权利</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，并甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">需承担</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">关于作品侵权违规所造成所有损失并赔偿</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6.4 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权向客户提供甲方所发布的肖像权或物权授权文件，但在这种情况下，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">应确保模特个人信息的隐私不被泄露。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">6.5 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权将甲方的作品中无法提供准确的肖像权或物权的作品作为编辑用途作品进行销售。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">七</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 费用</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.1 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">以以下方式支付甲方费用，所有的支付币种是以人民币（RMB）进行结算，费用计算方式</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">按照下述录用作品的交易形式（买断式录用、分成式录用）进行计算。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">7.2</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">买断式录用</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.2.1 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">即甲方上传符合乙方设计要求的作品，并同意乙方提出的买断录用报价</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，后</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">双方按照此价格对作品进行买断的交易形式。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.2.2 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方针对作品提</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">出的录用报价金额为税后价款，本协议</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">价款所涉及的个人所得税</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">由乙</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">方按照</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">国家法律规定进行</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">代缴</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">7.3 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">分成式录用</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.1</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方所录用的作品，均会经过自身加工与再处理后，在合作方或第三方平台进行但不限于广告、主题锁屏等投放形式获取收益，其所产生的收益将会通过分成的形式，以</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《分成式录用：分成渠道定价表》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的分成价格与甲方定期结算。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.2 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">因乙方合作的第三方平台的投放渠道、定价、投放效果不可控，甲方必须默认接收乙方的投放决策及分成定价，且乙方不对实际的投放渠道、投放效果数据、最终分成收益作任何保证。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.3 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">甲方的录用作品在某投放渠道分成单价，以作品录用后在该渠道投放产生数据的那一刻</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《分成式录用：分成渠道定价表》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的单价为准，按对应投放渠道的数据指标结算收益，直到该投放渠道下线。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.4 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方每一次渠道投放所使用的素材，可能来源于多名甲方所提供多个录用作品素材加工而成，在此情况下，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">各甲方将均分该渠道分成单价进行分成，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">并将该信息展示至录用订单处。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.5 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">甲方的录用作品，以及乙方对其进行一次</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">修改、编辑、剪辑、汇编、改编</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">后的素材，投放至渠道所产生的收益均会与作品甲方进行分成</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。但对修改后的录用作品素材再进行二级或多级加工产生的素材，其渠道投放收益将不再与甲方分成。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.3.6 当</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方在与合作第三方结算渠道投放收益时</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，由于作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">素材</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的质量问题</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">等原因，导致无法结算时，乙方有权要求甲方退还该渠道已分成给甲方的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，并有权优先</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">从</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">供稿人甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的收益里扣除</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">该收益</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.4</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《分成式录用：分成渠道定价表》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">是本协议不可分割的一部分，具有同等的法律效力</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。且乙方有权对</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《分成式录用：分成渠道定价表》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的内容不定时更新，并以公示的形式展示到</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">HelloRF </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，甲方应在作品录用时间前后及时关注</span><span style="color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">《分成式录用：分成渠道定价表》</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">信息。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.5</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> HelloRF 应当在每月 15 日~25 日</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">对</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">所有有效的</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">提现申请完成</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">付款，如甲方</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">不能提供提现金额</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">等额的增值税发票，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">狮圈儿</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt"> 将</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">代扣</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">个人</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">所得税。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.6 最低支付标准 300 元。 </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.7 如果在付款期间内，甲方版权费累计未能达到最低支付标准，甲方的收入将自动累计到下一个支付期。系统将会检查甲方的付款信息，甲方需要在</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">平台供稿人认证申请时提交</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">收款</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">的银行</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">账号信息，如因甲方的收款账号信息有误或无效，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">发生无法支取或产生费用等相关的问题和法律责任，由甲方单方承担。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.8 帐户取消和总结剩余：如果甲方因严重违规，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">有权关闭甲方的帐户，有权冻结甲方账户中剩余的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">收益费用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">。</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">7.9 乙方通过银行汇款、转账等方式向甲方支付款项，甲方应向乙方备案收款账号、寄送地址等。如甲方变更上述信息时，应及时通知乙方进行备案。否则，如因此引起的后果，应由甲方自行承担，乙方不承担任何责任。</span><br /><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5pt">7.10</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议中所涉及的全部收益均为税前价格，甲方所得款项应按有关规定由乙方代缴甲</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">方收入的个人所得税。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">八</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">保密协议</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">8.1 任何一方对于因签署或履行本协议而了解或接触到的商业秘密及其他机密资料和信息（以下简称“保密信息”）均应保守秘密；非经对方书面同意，任何一方不得向第三方泄露、给予或转让该等保密信息。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">8.2 除本协议规定之工作所需外，未经对方事先同意，不得擅自使用、复制对方的商标、标志、商业信息、技术及其他资料。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">九</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">违约责任</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">9.1 甲方依据本协议提供的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">素材的内容所引发的任何</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">包括但不限于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">所有权利主张、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">作品</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">素材权属争议或侵权纠纷，甲方应自行依法解决并对外承担法律责任，如因此给乙方或其他第三方造成损失的，甲方应承担赔偿责任。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">9.2 任何一方违反本协议的任何条款，均视为违约，守约方有权以书面通知要求违约方纠正其违约行为。若违约方在收到书面通知后10日内仍未改正的，守约方可解除本协议，并有权要求违约方赔偿守约方因此遭受的损失。</span></p><h1 style="font-size:14pt; line-height:241%; margin:17pt 0pt 16.5pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">章 </span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">其他</span></h1><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">10.1 本协议的成立、生效、履行、解释及争议的解决均应适用中华人民共和国法律</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">，且因本协议所发生的一切纠纷，由乙方所在地人民法院管辖</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">。倘</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">若</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">本协议之任何规定因与中华人民共和国的法律抵触而无效，则这些条款将尽可能接近本协议原条文意旨重新解析，且本协</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-weight:bold">议其它规定仍应具有完整的效力及效果。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10.2 本协议的部分条款被认定为无效、非法或不能执行的，并不影响其他条款的效力和合法性，并且双方应当以最接近于该条款意图的新条款替代被认定为无效、非法和不能执行的条款。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10.3 如乙方在本协议项下所运营的网站和/或平台和/或图库等产品发生更名，则本协议条款对更名后的网站和/或平台和/或图库等产品继续有效，双方在本协议项下的权利义务关系不发生改变。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10.4 本协议可能因国家政策、履行环境发生变化或乙方的需要而进行修改，乙方会将修改后的协议予以发布。若您对修改后的协议有异议的，请</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">停止认证平台供稿人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">、使用本网站，若您</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">认证成为平台供稿人</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">则</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">视为认可修改后的协议。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10.5</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议内容经双方充分协商后确定，为各方真实意思表示。</span><br /><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">10.6</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt">本协议所有条款的标题仅为阅读方便，本身并无实际涵义，不能作为本协议涵义解释的依据。</span></p></div><hr style="width:33%; height:1px; text-align:left" /><div id="_cmnt1" style="-aw-comment-author:'Administrator'; -aw-comment-datetime:'2019-04-16T16:37:00'; -aw-comment-initial:'A'"><p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; widows:0"><a href="#_cmntref1">[A1]</a><span style="font-family:等线; font-size:10.5pt">这些权利是否与我们有关？</span></p></div><div id="_cmnt2" style="-aw-comment-author:'Administrator'; -aw-comm